title: For My People Ministry - Videos
description:
The mission of For My People Ministry is to share God’s messages through His words and to prepare a people for the imminent return of Christ through repentance, reformation and victory over sin.

Our beliefs are based only on the Holy Bible and the Spirit of Prophecy as exemplified in the writings of Ellen G. White, who was a messenger of the Lord. This is the rule of our faith and practices, given to us by God through the inspiration of His Holy Spirit. We keep the Sabbath, according to the commandment in Exodus 20:8-11, which is Saturday, the seventh day of the week. We also look forward to Christ’s Second Coming. (Matthew 24:30; 1 Thessalonians 4:16-17; Revelation 1:7).
